_sText:
a map to run around and shoot cts with the ak only against the clock.

It is a set route, 29 CT to kill in the shortest time you can get

will help to improve your aim

>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>

create a server
load map "aim_office_time_an00biz"

Join Terrorist (does not work as CT)
stand on doormat in front of the door to start timer

shoot the CTs

once they are all killed timer will stop

rejoin terrorist team to restart
